        †⟨CppFormConstructor(#sortname, #csortvars?, #CONSTRUCTOR, #csorts?, FALSE)⟩
        †⟨CppFormMethodMake(#sortname, #csortvars?, #CONSTRUCTOR, #csorts?, FALSE)⟩
        †⟨CppFormMethodAs(#sortname, #csortvars?, #CONSTRUCTOR, FALSE)⟩
